</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='r'><span class='line'><span class="c1"># 从大连商品交易所网站抓取价格数据 数据源</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c1"># http://www.dce.com.cn/PublicWeb/MainServlet?action=Pu00011_search</span>
